column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) IS NOT # EXEC spExecuteSQL #'< a target = INFO href = http://skyserver.sdss.org/DR1#/en/tools/explore/obj.aspx? id = # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #> #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #< /a> # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z, s.z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID OIN SpecObj s ON p.specObjID = s.specObjID ORDER BY x.up_id##', @log = #, @filter = #
